results.title: Gordon River 3:15pm Afternoon Cruise - Upper Deck Window Seating
results.inclusions:
� Premium upper-deck window seating aboard the Harbour Master II,
� Full commentary by experienced local guides,
� Guided walking tour on Sarah Island,
� Rainforest boardwalk experience at Heritage Landing,
� Individually served Tasmanian-produce dinner,
� Complimentary tea and coffee throughout the cruise
results.highlights:
� Upper-deck window seats on the Harbour Master II for panoramic views,
� Visit Hells Gates, aquaculture farms, Sarah Island and the Gordon River wilderness,
� Individually served Tasmanian-produce dinner included while sailing,
� Access to indoor lounge, four outdoor viewing decks and full commentary,
� Family-owned, locally operated cruise with over 125 years of experience
results.additional_info:
Conditions:
Child rates apply for 5-16 years. Free travel for children under 5 years. Infants 0 - 4 yrs are not guaranteed seating. Individually prepared meals are included, served on trays to each customer (no queueing required) and include all Tasmanian produce (please advise the booking office of any food allergies). Cruises are not available on Christmas Day. Please advise the booking office directly of any dietary requirements by reaching 03 6471 7174. licensed bars on board with a full range of beverages and snacks available for purchase (limited EFTPOS signal - we accept cash). Allocated seating with access to all deck levels.
results.description:
The world heritage cruises strahan experience invites you to relax in the upper deck window seating aboard the Harbour Master II, gliding through Macquarie Harbour and into the serene Gordon River wilderness.

Departing at 15:15 from Strahan Wharf, this afternoon cruise weaves through rich convict-era history on Sarah Island, dramatic tidal entrance Hells Gates, aquaculture farms and boardwalks through a UNESCO-listed rainforest at Heritage Landing. Guests enjoy individually served Tasmanian-produce dinner and abundant views from recliner-style window seats.

Ideal for couples, nature lovers and travellers seeking a relaxed premium experience, this cruise is a refined way to discover Tasmania�s wild west coast in comfort and style.
results.short_description: Premium afternoon cruise with upper-deck window seats exploring Macquarie Harbour and the Gordon River from Strahan.
